title._content: Feu de la Falaise du Raz de Sein

description._content: Title: Feu de la Falaise du Raz de Sein Alternative Title: Light on the Cliffs of Raz du Sein Creator: Unknown Date: 1883 Series: Tome Cinquieme: Phares et Balises Place: Pointe du Raz, Finistere, France Description: The full title of the five-volume set is, Les travaux publics de la France par MM. F. Lucas et V. Fournie - Ed. Collignon - H. de Lagrene - Voisin Bey - E. Allard. Ouvrage publie sous les auspices de Ministere des travaux publics et sous la direction de M. Leonce Reynaud. This photograph is one of 50 plates in Public Works of France, Volume Five: Lighthouses and Beacons. Physical Description: 1 photographic print: collotype; 26 x 35 cm on 40 x 56 cm mount File: vault_folio_2_ta71_a4_1883_5_30_opt.jpg Rights: Please cite Southern Methodist University, Central University Libraries, DeGolyer Library when using this image file.
